              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Target of niobium metal (purity better than 99%)",
                " had an average thickness of 9.99mg/cm**2  +- 2%",
                " Target was rotated by 180 degrees in the",
                " middle of each experiment to reduce inhomogeneities",
                " assumed to be less than 2%. The niobium target",
                " was irradiated during 220 hours."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Energy and angular distributions of the protons",
                " from 24 to 164 degrees with a resolution of 15 degrees",
                " energy resolution is assumed to be better than 1.5 MeV"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PSD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " To discriminate protons deuterons in the CsI",
                " scintillator. The error for the identification is less",
                " than 2 %"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "PROPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "  48 proportional counters. Filling gas is",
